# Portal V2 dashboard tree (currently a plumbing stub; the real
# shadcn-admin scaffold lands in a later chunk).
#
# dist/ rules:
#   - Hashed Vite output (e.g. dist/assets/*) is generated and ignored.
#   - BUT keep dist/index.html as a committed stub so `go:embed` always
#     has something to embed on a fresh clone — go:embed fails the build
#     if the directory is empty. Same pattern as the legacy dashboard/.
#   - Also keep dist/.gitkeep (if added) so the directory itself survives.

dist/*
!dist/index.html
!dist/.gitkeep

# Generated by `npm install` once we wire shadcn-admin.
node_modules/
